data.title: Last Ride
data.meta_description:
The STA / TransAdelaide / Adelaide Metro 2000 class 'Jumbo' railcars scrapping began today, with trailer car 2116 being the first to take it's last ride from the Dry Creek depot to Sims at Gillman.
	
	Here, the convoy passes the BP at Dry Creek, en route from Dry Creek depot to SIMS Metals
